3. UPLOADING  / COMMITING / SUBMIT :
-------------------------------------
CREATE YOUR OWN GIT REPO:
initializing the folder is once per life .
put this in console:
git init 
--------------------------------------------
hint: (did u run the command while u r on home directory?)
that will creat a .git hiden folder repo on pc hdd location
on  :  /home/USERNAME/  .git
------------------------------------------------
PS:! i think that will auto-create a hosting point? 0.0
anyway , those are the console  commands:
------------------------------------------------
git status		    this is a kind of help and analyse
git add THE-FILENAME    this will synchro the file online
git commit              this will  submit your repo online


